data.description: Secluded well built Single story home with great level access near hwy 2.  no neighbors in the rear.  Central AC.  Attached two car garage.  Save on heating bill with the fireplace insert.  Re-roofed in 2021.  Vaulted ceiling in living room.  RV Parking available  Furnace updated in 2021.  Attic Fan. Property mostly cleared of trees.  Spacious shed in excellent condition with electric.  SEPTIC CERTIFICATION NEWLY COMPLETED!  House has a good offset from street  Easy to maintain landscaping.  High speed internet available (fiber run to the house)
